basics.label: Student
basics.summary: I am a PhD student in Computer Science at the University of Hawaii Manoa since Fall 2019, working on Deep Learning with Peter Sadowski. Before moving to UH, I worked on Natural language  processing, and adversarial music generation with of Anna Bosman, and Pieter Devilliers at the university of Pretoria.
